stereoCamera.py
	Helper class encapsulating the calculation of offaxis stereo
	settings (parallel axis asymmetric frustum perspective projection,
	see http://local.wasp.uwa.edu.au/~pbourke/projection/stereorender)
	The underlying equations and their implementation are by courtesy of 
	Paul Bourke.
stereoDemo.py
	Demo showing a rotating teapot in anaglyph oder shutter glasses 
	stereo mode depending on the command line argument.
